des: Begin every morning with an inspirational good morning phrase, followed by a compliment. It's never too early to hear you're gorgeous or to be inspired. Come back each day to hear a new quote that will jump start your day. You will never wake up on the wrong side of the bed with Good Morning Gorgeous.
